attributes.action: Hold an inquiry into Downing St event on 13 November 2020
attributes.additional_details: To ensure accountability and standards in public office, it is paramount that the alleged flat party is investigated. The public deserve to know the truth.
attributes.background:
Sue Gray conceded in her report that the alleged party in the Downing Street flat during the lockdown on 13th November 2020 has not been investigated by her or the police.

This is totally unacceptable and unfair on those who have been fined and held to account for lockdown breaches.
